cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.MM, cs.IR 

This paper is primarily focused on computer vision tasks, specifically object detection in low-resolution images. Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). Additionally, the paper proposes a novel framework that involves training a deep neural network, which falls under the category of artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also discusses the optimization of the network, which is related to machine learning (cs.LG). Furthermore, the paper involves image processing techniques, which can be categorized under multimedia (cs.MM) and information retrieval (cs.IR).
